<p><%= t(:hello).capitalize %>  <%= @resource.first_name%>&ensp;<%= @resource.last_name%>, We received a password reset request from your account. Please visit the following URL to reset your password:</p>
<p><%= link_to t('.password_change_link'), edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token, config: message['client-config'].to_s, redirect_url: message['redirect-url'].to_s).html_safe %></p>
<p>If the above URL does not work try copying and pasting it into your browser.</p>
<p>If you did not request a password reset, please contact us.</p>